					Full Description



		Softimat SA, (formerly known as Systemat SA), is a Belgium-based computer services provider. The Company offers various products and services, including the design and integration of networks, personal computers and servers, support and maintenance, helpdesk, remote management, business continuity and disaster recovery, hosting, Web design, enterprise resource planning (ERP) solutions, accounting software, e-commerce solutions, storage area networking and financing. The Company divides its activities into three divisions: hardware services, software services and real estate activities. As of December 31, 2011, Softimat SA had a number of subsidiaries, including Softimat Sud SA, Softimat Noord NV, POPSY SOFTWARE SA, Softimat Luxembourg SA, HTF SAS, Softimat Consulting SA and Infomat BV, among others. Through its subsidiaries, the Company is active in various countries, such as Belgium, France and Luxembourg.
» Full Overview of SYMA.BR







